      "role": "user",
      "content": "inventory ghosting... i get that, but i've had the team do a deep sweep of the warehouse and nothing is just \"sitting in a corner.\" everything is accounted for except for those few missing units. it's almost like they're vanishing during the actual transit through the aisles. what's the logic behind these tiny, irregular losses if there's no actual error in the scan?",
